OL,3,CIntense debate on Galloway National
OL,4,CPark plans ahead of consultation
OL,6,FA Dumfries and Galloway campaigner
OL,7,Fsays views on the future of a new
OL,8,FNational Park have become "very
OL,9,Fpolarised" between both sides of the
OL,10,Fdebate.
OL,12,FA 12-week public consultation is set
OL,13,Fto launch in November for people to
OL,14,Fshare their views on the proposals.
OL,15,FGalloway was chosen as the preferred
OL,16,Fsite out of a shortlist of five, in
OL,17,FJuly 2024.
