OL,3,CIntense debate on Galloway National
OL,4,CPark plans ahead of consultation
OL,6,FThe two national parks in Scotland are
OL,7,Fthe Cairgorms and the Loch Lomond &
OL,8,Fthe Trossachs - it has now been more
OL,9,Fthan 20 years since a new Scottish
OL,10,Farea was granted National Park status.
OL,12,FRob Lucas, from the Galloway National
OL,13,FPark Association, says he hopes the
OL,14,Fdebate on the plans is becoming "more
OL,15,Fmeasured".
OL,17,F"I think it's become very polarised
OL,18,Fand that's unfortunate. I sense we
OL,19,Fmight have turned a corner and the
OL,20,Fdebate is perhaps becoming a little
OL,21,Fmore measured."
