OL,3,CIntense debate on Galloway National
OL,4,CPark plans ahead of consultation
OL,6,FHe added: "I think a National Park
OL,7,Fmade in Galloway, for Galloway, would
OL,8,Freally give people in the area an
OL,9,Fopportunity to have a say in its
OL,10,Ffuture.
OL,12,F"The first simple thing is it puts
OL,13,FGalloway on the map and that means
OL,14,Fpeople are attracted to come here -
OL,15,Fpeople will be attracted to come and
OL,16,Fvisit. We have a worrying population
OL,17,Fdecline going on and we think a
OL,18,Fnational park can help address that."
