OL,6,FThe National Farmers Union Scotland
OL,7,Fhas said it is strongly opposed to the
OL,8,Fplans as it could create housing,
OL,9,Ftransport, access and planning issues
OL,10,Ffor local farmers.
OL,12,FWhereas Mairi Gougeon, Scotland's
OL,13,Frural affairs secretary, said the
OL,14,FGalloway bid detailed benefits of what
OL,15,FNational Park status would bring to
OL,16,Fthe region.
