OL,3,CIntense debate on Galloway National
OL,4,CPark plans ahead of consultation
OL,6,FDenise Brownlee, who started the 'No
OL,7,FGalloway National Park' campaign after
OL,8,Flistening to concerns from local
OL,9,Fpeople, believes there are wider
OL,10,Fissues in the area that need to be
OL,11,Faddressed.
OL,13,FShe said: "We have no facts, that's
OL,14,Fthe problem. There are no facts on the
OL,15,Fground of what will happen and what is
OL,16,Fcoming to this area if we become a
OL,17,FNational Park.
