OL,3,CIntense debate on Galloway National
OL,4,CPark plans ahead of consultation
OL,6,F"The issue is seasonal work. You can't
OL,7,Fget a mortgage. You can't rent a house
OL,8,Fbecause you cannot get a secure job.
OL,9,FThere's a knock on effect through
OL,10,Feverything.
OL,12,F"People seem to think here that it
OL,13,Fwill help with hospitality, already a
OL,14,Flot of the pubs, hotels and different
OL,15,Fthings are shutting a couple of days a
OL,16,Fweek. Not because they're lacking
OL,17,Fpeople wanting to come through the
OL,18,Fdoor, they're lacking staff."
