OL,3,CIntense debate on Galloway National
OL,4,CPark plans ahead of consultation
OL,6,FIn a statement, NatureScot, said: "We
OL,7,Frecognise that there are strong views
OL,8,Fon both sides of the argument for and
OL,9,Fagainst the Scottish Government's
OL,10,Fproposal of a new national park in
OL,11,FGalloway.
OL,13,F"NatureScot is committed to making
OL,14,Fsure that the public consultation
OL,15,Fprocess is inclusive, transparent and
OL,16,Fparticipatory, and that everyone has
OL,17,Fsufficient opportunity to respond to
OL,18,Fit."
